      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 4538204734068884366
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 4538204734068884367
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 4538204734068884368
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "The Light of Kareth never rests\u2014and neither do we."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884369
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "Kareth blesses the brave\u2014and you look like one who\u2019s known
          His gaze."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884370
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Every night is a trial of courage. Dawn is the reward.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884371
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "Justice doesn\u2019t sleep, even if we barely stand."
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884372
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: May Kareth guide our hands to justice...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884373
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: ...May His Light pierce every shadow...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884374
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: ...And may our blades never tremble before the innocent.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884375
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Hendrik received a letter from someone called Jonas, do you know anyone
          like that?
    - rid: 4538204734068884376
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Hello officer, i'm looking for your village chief. Do you know where
          is he?
    - rid: 4538204734068884377
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Can you tell me something about Kareth?
    - rid: 4538204734068884378
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: How are you today?
    - rid: 4538204734068884379
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: See you.
    - rid: 4538204734068884380
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Welcome in Stabury.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884381
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Unfortunately, the mayor has been gone for a few days.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884382
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: We wanted to look for him, but we can't leave the village without his
          consent, but I see that you were sent to help?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884383
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Yes, I want to find him. '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884384
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay, then I recommend talking to his wife. She lives in a house in
          the western part of the village.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884385
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I suspect bandits kidnapped him, but looking for them in the woods
          without any clues is like finding a needle in a haystack.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884386
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Why do you think so?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884387
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Because when are bandits most dangerous?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884388
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: At night?
    - rid: 4538204734068884389
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Winter?
    - rid: 4538204734068884390
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Well, you're right, but they are a real nuisance in winter.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884391
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Of course! Winter is, paradoxically, the best time for them.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884392
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Then they collect all the caravans going to the village.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884393
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: They sneak up and steal food and fuel.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884394
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I suspect Hendrik had something to do with it, but I have no proof.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884395
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Kareth watches over all who uphold the law.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884396
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "Justice is not mercy, and mercy is not weakness \u2014 that\u2019s
          what they teach us.\n"
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884397
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: As long as I wear this badge, I answer to him as much as to the village.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884398
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: You said Jonas?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884399
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Jonas Stonebend is the bandit leader in this part of the forest.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884400
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: They say that if you mess with him, at best he will only kill you,
          at worst all your loved ones.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884401
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: If this is true, then we must prepare for war.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884402
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I'll send a messenger to the city for support today, and you run away
          while you can, this is not your war.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884403
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: No, I came here to find the chief and I will do it.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884404
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: You must be very brave, or mad, if you want to face Jonas, who defied
          the gods.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884405
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I won't leave you without support, I can give you one of the weapons,
          the rest will be needed in the village.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884406
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: What do you prefer, a great axe, a spear or a bow?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884407
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Great axe is my favourite weapon.
    - rid: 4538204734068884408
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Spear, I have to be fast on this mission.
    - rid: 4538204734068884409
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Bow, I'll get rid of him before he notices me.
    - rid: 4538204734068884410
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Nothing, you'll find it more useful, I have a sword.
    - rid: 4538204734068884411
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: So honorably, take these potions, they will help you heal your wounds.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884412
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Thanks, any tips before the mission?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884413
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Don't get killed.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884414
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: And maybe one more, I saw a patrol of bandits nearby, maybe practice
          fighting on them and then try the rest.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884415
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: If you get their outfit, you might be able to infiltrate their camp
          without a fight and only get rid of the leader.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884416
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: That's a good tip. See you soon.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 4538204734068884417
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Let Kelvor guide your sword and Kareth your heart.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
